    "This enables a fast recovery from early rejections.",
    "If accepted, the process enters the post-verify phase, where the draft model continues generating tokens without interruption and the target model concurrently verifies them.",
    "A rejection during this phase triggers a return to pre-verify phase.By dynamically switching between these two phases, the PSD framework maintains uninterrupted utilization of both models and reduces idle time.",
    "However, we observe that this synchronization is fragile and can easily degrade when mobileside computation and network latency are not properly aligned.",
